org.ow2.proactive.resourcemanager.core.jmx.mbean

Class RuntimeDataMBeanImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.management.StandardMBean
      • org.ow2.proactive.resourcemanager.core.jmx.mbean.RuntimeDataMBeanImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DynamicMBean, MBeanRegistration, RuntimeDataMBean

    @PublicAPI
public class RuntimeDataMBeanImpl
extends StandardMBean
implements RuntimeDataMBean
    This class implements RuntimeDataMBean to expose the runtime data of the Resource Manager following the JMX standard for management. It provides a consistent view of the Resource Manager statistics.
    Since:
    ProActive Scheduling 1.1
    See Also:
    RuntimeDataMBean
